{"type":"text","timestamp":1773351624570,"sessionID":"ses_31c036d5affeENe71rAql6keLu","part":{"id":"prt_ce3fe2e4b0023emcdCxeErBZ0Z","sessionID":"ses_31c036d5affeENe71rAql6keLu","messageID":"msg_ce3fe2733001d0eYLkKvFi2x7q","type":"text","text":"Everything passes. Here's a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\n**Feature:** `status-json-output` — Add `--output json` support to the `wombo status` command.\n\n### Changes Made\n\n**`src/commands/status.ts`** (main implementation):\n- Added `outputFmt` optional parameter to `StatusOptions` interface\n- Added helper functions: `elapsedMs()`, `formatElapsed()`, `agentToJson()`, `buildStatusJson()`\n- `agentToJson()` — maps each agent to a structured JSON object including feature_id, branch, worktree, status, pid, retries, timing info (started_at, completed_at, elapsed_ms, elapsed_formatted), build_passed, error, activity, and effort_estimate_ms\n- `buildStatusJson()` — builds the full wave status JSON with: `wave_id`, `base_branch`, timestamps, elapsed time, config metadata, `is_complete` flag, `agents` array, and `summary` counts (total + counts by every AgentStatus)\n- Updated `cmdStatus()` to use `output()` helper — emits JSON when `--output json` is specified, falls back to the existing `printDashboard()` for text mode\n- When no active wave exists, emits structured JSON with `wave_id: null` via `outputMessage()`\n\n**`src/index.ts`** (wiring):\n- Passed `outputFmt: args.outputFmt` to `cmdStatus()` call\n\n### JSON Schema\n\nThe `--output json` flag produces:\n```json\n{\n  \"wave_id\": \"wave-2026-03-12-123\",\n  \"base_branch\": \"main\",\n  \"started_at\": \"2026-03-12T...\",\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-12T...\",\n  \"elapsed_ms\": 123456,\n  \"elapsed_formatted\": \"2h3m\",\n  \"max_concurrent\": 6,\n  \"model\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-20250514\",\n  \"interactive\": false,\n  \"is_complete\": false,\n  \"agents\": [\n    {\n      \"feature_id\": \"...\",\n      \"branch\": \"feature/...\",\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"elapsed_ms\": 45000,\n      ...\n    }\n  ],\n  \"summary\": {\n    \"total\": 5,\n    \"queued\": 1, \"installing\": 0, \"running\": 2,\n    \"completed\": 1, \"verified\": 1, \"failed\": 0,\n    \"merged\": 0, \"retry\": 0, \"resolving_conflict\": 0\n  }\n}\n```\n\nNo new dependencies were added. The implementation follows existing patterns from `features list` and `features show` commands.","time":{"start":1773351624569,"end":1773351624569}}}
